<p>â€”- â€œTo apply and direct this vast new potential of destructive energy excited the inventive genius of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leonardo%20da%20Vinci" title="Wikipedia: Leonardo da Vinci">Leonardo</a> as had few other enterprises.â€ â€”-</p>
