<p>Conorâ€™s hand moved to the radio for â€“when there is a clamor across the land, who turns a tin ear? My friends, libberuls may ask for equal time, but I, Tuck Eubanks, <em>am</em> equal time</p>
<p>â€“Conor, do we have to listen to this, this idiot?</p>
